name: Version 1.1.0.16
body: Fixed bugs, improved notifications and added dialog with no support for Karta Krakowska.

name: Version 1.1.0.15
body: Improved screen brightness during ticket control and fixed ticket sync bugs.

name: Version 1.1.0.14
body: Fixed null url shown in version info.

name: Version 1.1.0.13
body: Fixed bugs in settings page and added ticket localization.

name: Version 1.1.0.12
body: Improved UI and added English localization.

name: Version beta 1.0.6
body: Added option to restart app in settings and fixed missing accounts permissions on Lollipop.

name: Version beta 1.0.5
body: Renamed app to mobileKKM, improved registration process with instructions to complete process (#13), added help dialog on login page, added settings page with about page (#12) and fixed other bugs.

name: Version beta 1.0.4
body: Migrate to AndroidX libraries (#3), add going back in webapp instead closing the app (#7) and fix navbar not being removed on some older webview versions (mostly Lollipop).

name: Version beta 1.0.3
body: Remove contacts permission and logout automatically if the session has expired.

name: Version beta 1.0.2
body: Fix disclaimer not being dismissed after user selected "Don't show again".
